  "3115010": {
    "name": "Car Dealer Simulator: Prologue - Early Days",
    "steam_appid": 3115010,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Car Dealer Simulator Early Days is a free prologue to the full Car Dealer Simulator game.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Little Sam, the quirky owner of the business, will introduce you to its secrets. He’s not great at keeping things in order, so your task is to buy low, fix up, and sell high. In the full game, if you handle the initial tasks well, you’ll have the chance to take over the business, and then…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115010/extras/5e362b2c90348549cc4a3f8108d0b765.avif?t=1748944884\" width=630 height=166 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everything will be in your hands! Build a business that fulfills your customers’ automotive fantasies. From budget-friendly cars to extravagant rides, seize opportunities, hire the best, provide excellent service, and maximize profits. Grow your company day by day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115010/extras/da25100076ad3105d481a7bb8f65ba23.poster.avif?t=1748944884\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115010/extras/da25100076ad3105d481a7bb8f65ba23.webm?t=1748944884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115010/extras/da25100076ad3105d481a7bb8f65ba23.mp4?t=1748944884\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The key to achieving high profits lies in negotiating when buying old cars. Look for great deals, and during price haggling, stay firm and professional.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115010/extras/2817e06ed1db8305e33e68eee3cb500f.poster.avif?t=1748944884\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115010/extras/2817e06ed1db8305e33e68eee3cb500f.webm?t=1748944884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115010/extras/2817e06ed1db8305e33e68eee3cb500f.mp4?t=1748944884\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not all purchased cars are in working condition, so you’ll need to use a tow truck to transport them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115010/extras/44cbccf454a6c76bae81cc381f28e43e.poster.avif?t=1748944884\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115010/extras/44cbccf454a6c76bae81cc381f28e43e.webm?t=1748944884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115010/extras/44cbccf454a6c76bae81cc381f28e43e.mp4?t=1748944884\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every car requires diagnostics and preparation before being sold. At Little Sam’s request, you’ll perform your first mechanical and bodywork repairs. In the prologue, the available tools are quite limited.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115010/extras/9e60e5fb6bb374838e34ada0201ccd92.poster.avif?t=1748944884\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115010/extras/9e60e5fb6bb374838e34ada0201ccd92.webm?t=1748944884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115010/extras/9e60e5fb6bb374838e34ada0201ccd92.mp4?t=1748944884\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Presenting a car to the customer requires a few tricks. Washing, good photos, and an engaging advertisement will be your allies. Little Sam will guide you through tasks such as washing, taking photos, and creating a sales listing. Remember, customers buy with their eyes, so use the shine of the paint, a full tank, and quality photos to your advantage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115010/extras/8a8e9426786c8e8f4d11762a65233c2e.poster.avif?t=1748944884\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115010/extras/8a8e9426786c8e8f4d11762a65233c2e.webm?t=1748944884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115010/extras/8a8e9426786c8e8f4d11762a65233c2e.mp4?t=1748944884\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your profits will allow you to continually grow your company. In the prologue, you’ll have the chance to upgrade the car wash, while in the full game, you’ll unlock additional tools, repair zones, and the customer service office.</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 捷克语, 荷兰语, 日语, 韩语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 俄语, 简体中文, 泰语, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语, 越南语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
